# ThinkTwice — local environment template.
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (which is gitignored) and fill in the value.
#
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN
#   A long-lived token that lets the app's headless `claude -p` calls
#   authenticate with your Claude account.
#   Generate it with:   claude setup-token
#   Then paste the printed sk-ant-oat01-... value below.
#
#   NOTE: logging into the interactive `claude` CLI alone is NOT enough —
#   headless calls require this token, or every debate returns
#   "401 Invalid authentication credentials". The token is valid ~1 year.
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=
